	<Title>
		Colon cancer screening: At what age can you stop?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Colon cancer screening may have an upper age limit of effectiveness. What is it?
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		I&apos;m 76 years old and am wondering when it&apos;s no longer necessary to get colon cancer screening? Is there an upper age limit?
	</Question>
